    "□Before continuing towards the proof of Proposition 7.2, let us introduce some regions that will be used often below.Recall that for any R > 0 we denote by B R = {x ∈ R 2: ∥x∥ ∞ ≤ R} the closed box of side length 2R centered on the origin.",
